The general Hölder inequality for three functions $f, g, h$ states that $\|f \cdot g \cdot h\|_r \leq \|f\|_p \cdot \|g\|_q \cdot \|h\|_s$ where $\frac{1}{p} + \frac{1}{q} + \frac{1}{s} = \frac{1}{r}$.

